            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>
                </ab>
                
                <p>                    
                    <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vaṉa-c-cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-ku<supplied reason="lost">lōt</supplied>tu<supplied reason="lost">ṅka</supplied>-cōḻa-<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>varkku yāṇtu Irāṇṭ-āvatu
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    Uttuṅka <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> ṭukuka<choice><unclear>ṟa</unclear><unclear>ṟ</unclear></choice>-kūṟṟattu-p pērakaḻiyil irukkum puttūr-uṭaiyā<choice><orig>n</orig><reg>ṉ</reg></choice> <seg type="aksara"><seg type="component" subtype="body"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="component"/></seg>e</seg> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ā<choice><orig>n</orig><reg>ṉ</reg></choice> <hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vatāṉam Iṭṭa paṭi y-āvatu
                </p>
                <p>
                    Eṅkaḷ pitākkaḷ koṇṭ-uṭaiya kāṇi-y-āy varukiṟa Ip-pērakaḻiyilē civa-liṅka-p-piratiṭṭaiyum paṇṇi Upāṉāti-tūpi
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>-puriyantam-āka-t tiru-k-kaṟṟaḷiyuñ cātti viṉāyaka-p-piḷḷaiyār <hi rend="grantha">kṣetra</hi>pāla-p-piḷḷaiyār mutal-āṉa cilar m<choice><orig>u</orig><reg>ū</reg></choice>rttaṅkaḷu<unclear>m</unclear> Eḻunt-aruḷ<supplied reason="lost">uvit</supplied>tu tiru-mēṉi nāyaṉmāraiyum Eḻunt-aruḷuvittu I<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>nāy<choice><sic><unclear>u</unclear></sic><corr>a</corr></choice>ṉār Aḻa <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> t<supplied reason="lost">ē</supplied>vatāṉam patināl <unclear>aṭi</unclear>yum vilakkaṭ<unclear>i</unclear>yumāna kōlāl Ivv-ūr mēlai-k kaḻaṉiyiṟ kāṟ-ceyyum kiḻai-k kaḻaṉiyiṟ kāṟ-ceyyum Ik-kōlāl                    
                </p>
                
